    	  <h1 align="left">About Amazing Grace - The Story</h1>
    	  <p>Lynne Samways Hiltz, wife of Primate Fred Hiltz, reads the story behind the hymn, &quot;Amazing Grace.&quot; You can watch the whole story at once, or in separate chapters. These sunny summer scenes were filmed along Lake Ontario, at the Scarborough Bluffs.</p>
    	  <p>Mrs. Samways Hiltz also sang the hymn a cappella. <a href="/amazinggrace/videos/lsh.htm">Watch the video here</a>.</p>
